<item>
            <title>[SOLR-2651] The new SolrCore#reload method does not create a ZkSolrResourceLoader in ZooKeeper mode</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-2651</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;this is a trunk bug&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;reload is hard wired to simply make a SolrResourceLoader - this means that in ZooKeeper mode, changes to config are not picked up on a reload - instead you would get any local configs.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12514004">SOLR-2651</key>
